## Description {#details}

A symbol table used for function &#91;IR&#93;PGO name look-up with keys (such as pointers, md5hash values) to the function.

A function&#39;s &#91;IR&#93;PGO name or name&#39;s md5hash are used in retrieving the profile data of the function. See <code><a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a1b3e6af13e7130b5bd9994948ec48ccd">getIRPGOFuncName()</a></code> and <code>getPGOFuncName</code> methods for details how &#91;IR&#93;PGO name is formed.

Definition at line 460 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/profiledata/instrprof-h">InstrProf.h</a>.
